Sure, here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "teri":

1. *Teri* loptu u gol. (Score the ball in the goal.)
2. Ona *teri* svog psa u parku. (She walks her dog in the park.)
3. Moramo *terati* stoku s polja. (We have to drive the livestock from the field.)
4. Uvek *teram* sebe da budem bolja. (I always push myself to be better.)
5. Oni često *teraju* šalu na svoj račun. (They often make jokes at their own expense.)
6. Njih dvojica se stalno *teraju* u raznim igrama. (The two of them constantly challenge each other in various games.)
7. *Teri* nam taj novac, ne znaš koliko će nam značiti. (Lend us that money, you don't know how much it will mean to us.)
8. Oni su uspeli da *isteraju* neprijatelje iz grada. (They managed to drive the enemies out of the city.)

I hope these examples help!